<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>RubriCheck AI | Assignment Feedback Before You Submit</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/RubriCheck%20Logo.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { activePage: 'home', landingAnchors: true }) %>

  <main class="landing-page product-home">
    <section class="landing-hero product-hero" id="top">
      <div class="container landing-hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy-block reveal-on-scroll">
          <p class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-icon">AI</span> Rubric-aware assignment review</p>
          <h1>RubriCheck AI</h1>
          <p class="hero-tagline">AI-powered assignment feedback before you submit.</p>
          <p class="hero-copy">
            Upload your brief, rubric, and draft on the analysis page. RubriCheck AI checks your work against the rubric and returns clear priorities, a checklist, and follow-up help.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/upload">Analyze Assignment</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#demo">View Example</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <article class="hero-product-panel hero-visual-panel reveal-on-scroll" aria-label="RubriCheck AI preview">
          <img class="hero-illustration" src="/images/rubricheck-hero-illustration.png" alt="Student reviewing AI assignment feedback on a laptop">
          <div class="hero-floating-card readiness-float">
            <span>Readiness</span>
            <strong>75%</strong>
            <div class="stat-progress green"><span style="width: 75%;"></span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-floating-card priority-float">
            <span>Next step</span>
            <strong>Fix rubric gaps</strong>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="landing-section compact-section problem-section" id="problem">
      <div class="container story-grid">
        <div class="section-heading align-left reveal-on-scroll">
          <p class="section-kicker">The Problem</p>
          <h2>Students lose marks when rubric requirements are missed.</h2>
          <p>
            A draft can look complete but still miss evidence, structure, citation, or explanation criteria. RubriCheck AI helps students catch those gaps before submission.
          </p>
        </div>

        <figure class="illustration-card compact-illustration reveal-on-scroll">
          <img src="/images/rubricheck-analysis-illustration.png" alt="AI analysing assignment documents and rubric checklist">
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="landing-section compact-section workflow-section" id="how-it-works">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading reveal-on-scroll">
          <p class="section-kicker">How It Works</p>
          <h2>From upload to feedback and reminders</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="simple-workflow-grid full-process-grid reveal-on-scroll" aria-label="RubriCheck AI workflow">
          <article><span>1</span><h3>Upload Files</h3><p>Add the assignment brief, marking rubric, and student draft.</p></article>
          <article><span>2</span><h3>Extract Text</h3><p>The system reads the uploaded PDF, DOCX, or TXT documents.</p></article>
          <article><span>3</span><h3>Retrieve Rubric Context</h3><p>RAG finds relevant rubric and document chunks from ChromaDB.</p></article>
          <article><span>4</span><h3>Gemini Analysis</h3><p>Gemini compares the draft against the retrieved rubric context.</p></article>
          <article><span>5</span><h3>Structured Feedback</h3><p>Students receive scores, priorities, checklist items, and follow-up chat.</p></article>
          <article><span>6</span><h3>Telegram Reminder</h3><p>Students can enable n8n-powered Telegram reminders after analysis.</p></article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="landing-section compact-section demo-section" id="demo">
      <div class="container preview-layout">
        <div class="section-heading align-left reveal-on-scroll">
          <p class="section-kicker">Example AI Feedback</p>
          <h2>A cleaner way to understand what to fix first.</h2>
          <p>This is a visual preview only. Use the analysis page to upload real files and generate your own feedback.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/upload">Start Real Analysis</a>
        </div>

        <div class="example-feedback-panel reveal-on-scroll" aria-label="Example AI feedback preview">
          <div class="feedback-metric-grid demo-metric-grid">
            <article class="feedback-stat-card">
              <span>Completion</span>
              <strong class="blue-text">75%</strong>
              <div class="stat-progress"><span style="width: 75%;"></span></div>
            </article>
            <article class="feedback-stat-card centered">
              <span>Readiness</span>
              <strong class="readiness-badge">Needs Improvement</strong>
              <small>Review before submission</small>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="feedback-preview-columns">
            <article>
              <h3>Top Priorities</h3>
              <ol class="priority-list">
                <li><span>1</span>Add clearer evidence for rubric claims.</li>
                <li><span>2</span>Improve explanation depth in key sections.</li>
                <li><span>3</span>Check citations and formatting.</li>
              </ol>
            </article>

            <article>
              <h3>Checklist</h3>
              <ul class="clean-checklist">
                <li><span aria-hidden="true"></span>All rubric points addressed</li>
                <li><span aria-hidden="true"></span>Examples support each claim</li>
                <li><span aria-hidden="true"></span>References are complete</li>
              </ul>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="landing-section compact-section reminder-flow-section" id="reminders">
      <div class="container reminder-compact">
        <div class="section-heading align-left reveal-on-scroll">
          <p class="section-kicker">Telegram Reminder</p>
          <h2>Turn feedback into submission reminders.</h2>
          <p>After analysis, students can enable Telegram reminder support using the existing n8n-ready reminder workflow.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/reminder">Enable After Analysis</a>
        </div>

        <figure class="illustration-card compact-illustration reveal-on-scroll">
          <img src="/images/rubricheck-reminder-illustration.png" alt="AI feedback connected to reminder notification workflow">
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer product-footer">
    <div class="container footer-content">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <img class="footer-logo" src="/images/RubriCheck%20Logo.png" alt="RubriCheck AI logo">
        <strong>RubriCheck AI</strong>
      </div>
      <p>Built for C240. Powered by Gemini, RAG, and n8n.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
